Paper: hep-th/9307195

Date: 1993-07-31

Title: On the Chiral Fermions in the Twistor--Like Formulation of D=10

Heterotic StringAuthors: D. Sorokin and M. Tonin

Comments: 10 pages, LaTeX, DFPD/93/TH/52

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B326 (1994) 84-88

An n=8 worldsheet superfield action is proposed for describing chiralfermions in the twistor-like formulation of an N=1, D=10 heterotic superstring.